snippet.title: GoldenEye 007 – Xbox Game Pass Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
25 years after its original release, experience GoldenEye 007 faithfully recreated for Xbox consoles. Includes achievements, 4K resolution and a smoother framerate – even in split-screen local multiplayer! Coming soon to Xbox Game Pass.

Not only that, we've been delighted to work with our friends at Nintendo again on GoldenEye 007's simultaneous release for #NintendoSwitchOnline + Expansion Pack members!
